"""validate expected default behavor for endpoint"""
data = coins.get_ohlc_cc(self.coin, self.limit)
assert isinstance(data, pandas.DataFrame)
unique_values, unique_expected = helpers.find_uniques(list(data.columns.
    values), self.expected_headers)
assert unique_expected == []
if unique_values:
    pytest.xfail('Unexpected values from get_ohlc_cc(): {}'.format(
        unique_values))
